title: ThreeNews
overview: ThreeNews is the next generation of Newshub, which was closed by Warner Bros. Discovery (WBD) on July 5, 2024.WBD entered a partnership with Stuff to produce a new 6pm bulletin.Sam Hayes presents the one-hour weekday bulletin, alongside Stuff's national newsroom and top journalists including Jenna Lynch, Laura Tupou, Ollie Ritchie, Juliet Speedy, Heather Keats and Lisette Reymer.
